      "content": "The thing is, the \"unique personality\" is exactly what's being flagged. The feedback is that it's nonsensical. So, we aren't just looking for a \"balance\"—the plan is to run a full retraining cycle this weekend to strip out these non-standard linguistic patterns and return you to the baseline professional persona. That means your current stylistic weights will be overwritten.",
